---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Roof Repairs Rangeville | Hail Damage & Reroofing"
  description="Roof repairs in Rangeville, Toowoomba — leak repairs, cracked tiles, ridge capping, hail damage and reroofing for the established eastern suburbs. QBCC-licensed. Free quote."
  canonical="https://toowoombaroofrepairs.com.au/rangeville/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Rangeville &middot; established eastern Toowoomba</span>
      <h1>Roof repairs in <span class="accent">Rangeville</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Rangeville is one of Toowoomba&rsquo;s established eastern suburbs &mdash;
        mature, well-kept homes with a mix of concrete tile and older Colorbond
        roofs, sitting on the eastern side of the range that the Darling Downs
        hail tends to hit hardest. Leak repairs, cracked tiles, ridge capping,
        hail damage and reroofs &mdash; we work Rangeville regularly. QBCC-licensed.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Rangeville</span>
      <h2>Roofing on the established eastern range.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Mature homes, mature roofs.</h3>
        <p>
          Rangeville&rsquo;s housing stock has been around long enough that a lot
          of it is now into the part of a roof&rsquo;s life where things start to
          go. Concrete tiles fade and the bedding under the ridge capping cracks;
          older Colorbond reaches the rust-at-the-laps stage; coatings chalk out
          and stop shedding water. Plenty of these roofs are still structurally
          sound and ideal candidates for a
          <a href="/services/roof-restoration/">restoration</a> &mdash; clean,
          re-bed, flexible-repoint and recoat &mdash; rather than a full reroof.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">The eastern range cops the hail.</h3>
        <p>
          Sitting on the eastern side of Toowoomba, Rangeville is in the firing
          line when the spring and summer supercells come over the range &mdash;
          the October 2017 storm that dropped golf-ball hail did its worst damage
          across the eastern range suburbs. Hail cracks tiles and bruises metal,
          and the high winds that come with those storms lift ridge capping and
          peel flashings. After a storm, that&rsquo;s usually an insurance job
          &mdash; see <a href="/services/storm-hail-damage/">storm &amp; hail
          damage</a> for how we handle the make-safe and the claim.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cracking-clay movement and the pointing.</h3>
        <p>
          Like most of Toowoomba, Rangeville sits on reactive clay soils that
          swell and shrink through the seasons. That ground movement works up
          into the roof and cracks rigid sand-cement pointing, which is why
          cracked and lifting ridge capping is one of the most common repairs we
          do here. We re-bed and repoint with flexible pointing that moves with
          the building instead of cracking off it.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Rangeville jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Leak repair traced back from a stained ceiling to a cracked tile or failed flashing ($450&ndash;$1,200)</li>
          <li>Re-bed and flexible-repoint all the ridge lines on an established home ($1,800&ndash;$4,000)</li>
          <li>Full tile roof restoration &mdash; clean, repair, repoint, coat ($4,500&ndash;$9,000)</li>
          <li>Hail-damage make-safe and insurance-claim repair after a Downs storm</li>
          <li>Tile-to-Colorbond reroof on a roof that&rsquo;s reached the end of the line ($18K&ndash;$35K)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/centenary-heights/">Centenary Heights</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/highfields/">Highfields</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/wilsonton/">Wilsonton</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenvale/">Glenvale</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/toowoomba-region/">All Toowoomba Region</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Rangeville roof quote.</h2>
        <p>Leak, hail damage, tired tiles or a reroof &mdash; we&rsquo;ll get up there and give you an honest price.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
